1
00:00:33,708 --> 00:00:37,418
[JEDI MURMURING]

2
00:00:55,166 --> 00:00:56,166
[BEEPS]

3
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:58,580
[DOOR OPENS, CLOSES]

4
00:01:11,458 --> 00:01:13,078
[BEEPING]

5
00:01:13,166 --> 00:01:15,626
[ELECTRONIC VOICE]
<i>Archive memory access.</i>

6
00:01:15,708 --> 00:01:18,498
<i>Please enter security clearance code.</i>

7
00:01:18,583 --> 00:01:20,543
[BEEPING]

8
00:01:20,625 --> 00:01:23,745
[ELECTRONIC VOICE]
<i>Code accepted, Master Sifo-Dyas.</i>

9
00:01:25,833 --> 00:01:27,173
<i>Planet Kamino.</i>

10
00:01:28,666 --> 00:01:30,166
[BEEPING]

11
00:01:30,916 --> 00:01:33,666
[ELECTRONIC VOICE]
<i>Kamino location deleted.</i>

12
00:01:35,333 --> 00:01:39,043
<i>Kamino archive data deleted.</i>

13
00:01:55,458 --> 00:01:58,328
[CHATTERING]

14
00:02:00,375 --> 00:02:03,875
What's causing all the excitement,
Master Jocasta?

15
00:02:03,958 --> 00:02:05,708
Your apprentice.

16
00:02:05,791 --> 00:02:06,791
Qui-Gon?

17
00:02:06,875 --> 00:02:11,745
Yes, it would seem
he has encountered a Sith Lord,

18
00:02:11,833 --> 00:02:15,173
or so he claimed to the Jedi High Council.

19
00:02:15,666 --> 00:02:17,786
Where was this encounter?

20
00:02:18,291 --> 00:02:23,171
Tatooine. Yes, I think that was it.

21
00:02:23,250 --> 00:02:26,290
Deep in the Outer Rim, of course.

22
00:02:26,375 --> 00:02:31,455
Qui-Gon Jinn always had
such an active imagination.

23
00:02:31,541 --> 00:02:34,041
As did you, Dooku.

24
00:02:34,541 --> 00:02:39,581
A quality valued less and less
in these great halls.

25
00:02:47,833 --> 00:02:51,633
[CHATTERING]

26
00:02:53,291 --> 00:02:55,461
I guess word travels fast.

27
00:02:55,958 --> 00:03:00,208
Well, your statements to the Council
were rather surprising.

28
00:03:01,833 --> 00:03:02,963
[DOOKU] Qui-Gon.

29
00:03:04,041 --> 00:03:05,381
Master.

30
00:03:06,583 --> 00:03:08,833
I heard of your report to the Council.

31
00:03:09,666 --> 00:03:13,286
Tell me about this mysterious attacker
on Tatooine.

32
00:03:13,791 --> 00:03:19,211
I encountered a highly skilled warrior,
one obviously trained in the Jedi arts.

33
00:03:19,291 --> 00:03:21,921
And you believe it was a Sith Lord?

34
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,170
Yes.

35
00:03:23,250 --> 00:03:27,710
I gather the Council was not eager
to validate that conclusion?

36
00:03:27,791 --> 00:03:30,081
No, they were not, Master.

37
00:03:30,583 --> 00:03:34,383
I've been warning them about
the coming darkness for years,

38
00:03:34,875 --> 00:03:36,745
never to be taken seriously.

39
00:03:37,250 --> 00:03:43,130
Speaking on behalf of the Council,
there's no reason to cause undue alarm.

40
00:03:43,208 --> 00:03:44,998
So, you doubt his claim?

41
00:03:45,875 --> 00:03:47,705
No. I do not.

42
00:03:48,333 --> 00:03:53,633
But the wisdom of the Council is
to be cautious until we know more.

43
00:03:54,708 --> 00:03:56,668
Master Yaddle is right about one thing.

44
00:03:57,916 --> 00:04:00,166
A Sith Lord is not to be trifled with.

45
00:04:00,791 --> 00:04:05,331
And I will not be there to protect you,
my old Padawan.

46
00:04:06,083 --> 00:04:07,963
You need not worry, Master.

47
00:04:08,041 --> 00:04:09,791
Obi-Wan fills that role now.

48
00:04:10,291 --> 00:04:13,081
He acquits himself quite well.

49
00:04:13,875 --> 00:04:16,995
That's good.
I should like to meet him someday.

50
00:04:17,916 --> 00:04:19,916
You're always singing his praises.

51
00:04:40,083 --> 00:04:43,293
Master Dooku, are you all right?

52
00:04:44,375 --> 00:04:49,035
They grow up so fast, our students.

53
00:04:50,041 --> 00:04:53,421
Yes, it is the way of things.

54
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:54,500
Indeed.

55
00:04:56,125 --> 00:04:58,125
I must take my leave.

56
00:05:54,416 --> 00:05:58,376
I used to bring Qui-Gon here as a boy.

57
00:06:00,333 --> 00:06:02,963
He was fascinated with this tree.

58
00:06:03,791 --> 00:06:09,751
Having been born here on Coruscant,
a planet of steel and stone...

59
00:06:11,916 --> 00:06:13,956
he knew nothing like it.

60
00:06:15,958 --> 00:06:21,418
The Council is leaving for Naboo.
The funeral is to be held there.

61
00:06:23,041 --> 00:06:25,001
[THUNDER RUMBLING]

62
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:28,630
I doubt I will be pleasant company.

63
00:06:29,791 --> 00:06:32,041
You hold them accountable?

64
00:06:35,958 --> 00:06:39,128
Qui-Gon Jinn has become one
with the Force.

65
00:06:43,083 --> 00:06:44,833
It is time to let him go.

66
00:06:45,958 --> 00:06:47,418
And you can do this?

67
00:06:50,333 --> 00:06:52,003
What choice have I?

68
00:06:54,375 --> 00:06:58,075
[THUNDER RUMBLING]

69
00:08:05,625 --> 00:08:07,995
[CONTROLS BEEPING]

70
00:08:11,833 --> 00:08:13,253
[SHIP POWERS DOWN]

71
00:08:20,125 --> 00:08:21,875
You've gone too far!

72
00:08:22,625 --> 00:08:25,285
I don't know what you mean.

73
00:08:25,375 --> 00:08:28,995
Qui-Gon Jinn.
You allowed Maul to kill him.

74
00:08:30,083 --> 00:08:32,503
You lost an apprentice, and so did I.

75
00:08:33,583 --> 00:08:36,423
All in service of our greater goals.

76
00:08:41,875 --> 00:08:45,495
The galaxy will not be remade
without sacrifice.

77
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:49,170
He could've been a powerful ally.

78
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:51,420
For you, perhaps.

79
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:54,080
[DOOKU] You question my loyalty?

80
00:08:54,958 --> 00:08:55,958
Always.

81
00:08:56,541 --> 00:08:59,171
I have done everything you asked.

82
00:09:00,166 --> 00:09:03,626
And I will ask more of you,
if we are to succeed.

83
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:08,960
Sifo-Dyas, Kamino, the Clones.

84
00:09:09,791 --> 00:09:13,671
I have betrayed everyone
and everything I know.

85
00:09:14,250 --> 00:09:18,540
[SIDIOUS] No, you have been loyal
to a greater cause.

86
00:09:19,708 --> 00:09:24,248
How many have died because of my actions?

87
00:09:24,875 --> 00:09:26,825
Such is the price of freedom.

88
00:09:27,666 --> 00:09:28,666
[YADDLE] No!

89
00:09:30,291 --> 00:09:33,921
This ends here, Sith Lord.

90
00:09:36,166 --> 00:09:38,496
So, I have been betrayed?

91
00:09:38,583 --> 00:09:39,583
No!

92
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:51,500
Dooku, step to me.
Whatever your crimes are, help me now.

93
00:09:52,250 --> 00:09:55,080
Then you heard? You know.

94
00:09:56,375 --> 00:09:58,745
That does not matter.

95
00:10:00,166 --> 00:10:01,166
Don't believe her.

96
00:10:03,375 --> 00:10:08,165
Whatever lies he's told you,
whatever you have done,

97
00:10:08,833 --> 00:10:12,883
you can make up for it now
by bringing him to justice.

98
00:10:13,833 --> 00:10:15,793
[SIDIOUS] Remember what you told me.

99
00:10:16,958 --> 00:10:22,828
The Jedi blindly serve a corrupt Senate
that fails the Republic it represents.

100
00:10:25,125 --> 00:10:29,535
Do you want to prove your loyalty?
Kill her!

101
00:10:34,083 --> 00:10:36,503
There is still a chance
to make things right.

102
00:10:40,541 --> 00:10:41,541
I'm afraid...

103
00:10:42,791 --> 00:10:44,501
I know you are.

104
00:10:47,916 --> 00:10:50,536
I'm afraid it is too late.

105
00:10:50,625 --> 00:10:51,625
[LIGHTSABER IGNITES]

106
00:10:54,333 --> 00:10:55,333
No.

107
00:11:39,916 --> 00:11:42,326
[YADDLE] I am on your side, Dooku.

108
00:11:43,375 --> 00:11:46,785
I stepped down from my position
on the Council.

109
00:11:49,166 --> 00:11:51,536
You were right about so many things.

110
00:11:52,541 --> 00:11:53,961
The Council should've listened.

111
00:11:55,875 --> 00:11:58,285
Qui-Gon did not have to die.

112
00:12:06,375 --> 00:12:07,375
[SIDIOUS CACKLES]

113
00:12:19,833 --> 00:12:22,133
[DOOKU] Running back to your Council?

114
00:12:25,583 --> 00:12:27,633
It is you who has run, Dooku,

115
00:12:28,833 --> 00:12:31,673
into the arms of evil.

116
00:12:56,666 --> 00:12:59,916
[SIDIOUS]
You have done well, my apprentice.

117
00:13:03,458 --> 00:13:06,788
Rise, my friend.

118
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,000
Master.

119
00:13:11,041 --> 00:13:12,461
[RUMBLING]

120
00:14:00,125 --> 00:14:04,575
I want only to bring peace and order
to the galaxy.

121
00:14:06,291 --> 00:14:12,331
Already so many have suffered
for what you call "order".

122
00:14:13,791 --> 00:14:19,211
Then let me give you peace, Master Yaddle.

123
00:14:25,333 --> 00:14:26,333
[LIGHTSABER IMPACTS]

